vision.voltsofdoom.coresystem.universal.resource

Class VODJsonReader

  • java.lang.Object
    • vision.voltsofdoom.coresystem.universal.resource.VODJsonReader

  • public class VODJsonReader
extends java.lang.Object
    A handy class for reading the contents of .json files. Should use convenience methods in Gson ( eg getAsString and getAsInteger ) to get the contents of obj ( obtained by getObj ) as your wanted type. For example:

    double myDouble = obj.getAsDouble()

    You could then append .toString to the end if you so wished.
    Author:
    GenElectrovise
